            "Header": "Reap the Reward",
            "HeadingParagraphs": [
              "Reap the Reward was the first complete game prototype I created using the Unity Engine.",
              "This 2D dungeon-crawler was designed to test out the implementation of state-based character AI."
            ],
            "Subsections": [
              {
                "Type": "ImageSection",
                "Image": {
                  "Name": "Reap-The-Reward-Thumbnail.png"
                },
                "WrappedParagraphs": [
                  "Reap the Reward's level design was based on the 2D platformer <em>Wario Land 4</em> where the player must return to the start to complete each level.",
                  "<br>",
                  "A blend of enemy combat and puzzle-solving allow the player to progress to the bottom of a dungeon to collect treasure."
                ]
              },
